						               													<description>Noah's Ark game Two by Two. It's up to you to save the animals! There's no age limit on fun with this family game that tells the story of Noah's faith and reinforces his long-ago mission to do God's will. First you must gather the animals into the ark! Then you must journey through the treacherous waters and land safely on Mt. Ararat! The journney is filled with perils- and rewards, too! Beware of the lightening bolt! Be thankful for a Rainbow! The game casts each player in the roles of Noah and his family. Play the PRECIOUS MOMENTS Noah's Ark game with family and friends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player take an ark card and a characture playing piece. As players travel the game they will recreate the story of Noah and the Ark and collect animals as they go. Spin the spinner and move clockwise around the outer path of the game board. As a plyer lands of a colored space, the player may collect the animal associated with that color and place it on their ark card. A player landing on a sun space can collect any animal. Play continues until a player collects all 8 animals (2 of each kind), and immediately move back to start.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If during the game a player lands on a lightening bolt he must move 3 spaces back. Any player reaching start withou all 8 animals, must go around the outside of the board and continue until all 8 animals are collected.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Once a player has all of the animals and has moved back to start, he will spin and move along the inner trail. This path follows Noah's trip across the raging water. It is filled with perils just like Noah's journey. When the player reaches Mt. Ararat, he continues in turn to spin the spinner and unload his ark based on the number spun. When all of a player's animals are unloaded, the player contiunes to spin in turn and help others unload their animals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
